{"tid":2156693,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"川普女婿證實與Kanye West會面  策略師指共和黨試圖分散非裔選票","createTime":"2020-08-14T15:11:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T16:07:40.000Z","uid":28765,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c88dc9a37d70713a58c909c18ef7f9b3ae59d593","tid":2156693,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T15:11:19.000Z","msg":"2020-08-14 17:24:32<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕日前傳出美國總統川普（Donald Trump）女婿、白宮顧問庫許納（Jared Kushner）密會意圖角逐總統一職的饒舌歌手肯伊威斯特（Kanye West），庫許納在13日證實這項消息，提到2人對政策進行普通的對談，並未對肯伊威斯特的參選做過多的討論。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，肯伊威斯特日前向媒體透露，自己在科羅拉多州時，曾與庫許納和妻子伊凡卡（Ivanka Trump）會面。庫許納表示，自己和肯伊威斯特進行了友好的對談，但也強調，除了科羅拉多州的會面外，2人沒有進行其他討論。<br />\n<br />\n庫許納指出，肯伊威斯特和自己已認識10年，2人經常談論不同議題，肯伊威斯特對於這個國家有許多優秀的想法，這也是他試圖投入選舉的原因。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨則認為，肯伊威斯特的參選是試圖分散非裔民眾的選票，民主黨也將庫許納和肯伊威斯特的會面，稱是肯伊威斯特和共和黨合作的證據。民主黨策略師弗格森（Jesse Ferguson）表示，這是一種絕望的策略，因為川普團隊知道自己無法在正面對決中獲勝。<br />\n<br />\n......<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3260246\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3260246&d=NZlAC2w8bMplDXSravNUcYRM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=389aad70\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3260246&h=9ce527a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3260246</a>"},{"pid":"83a6009fb2199da364c80b6e22c19adc72a3b3f3","tid":2156693,"uid":59818,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T15:12:19.000Z","msg":"英國方國珊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0477667fd8e985224984bd58dbff6b4dc7d46fb9","tid":2156693,"uid":59818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"83a6009fb2199da364c80b6e22c19adc72a3b3f3","tid":2156693,"uid":59818,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T15:12:19.000Z","msg":"英國方國珊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T15:12:43.000Z","msg":"美"},{"pid":"4bcae2f5e29386b378a6d99c1c2b07ed63e3c24e","tid":2156693,"uid":61914,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T15:14:05.000Z","msg":"即係搵人幫手鎅走Joe biden啲票?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1530878f8e1580133b271e5e3e28444e5fc326e9","tid":2156693,"uid":47144,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T15:19:19.000Z","msg":"𠝹走年輕一代已經唔同晒格局<br />\n<br />\n美國後生嗰輩多數係左翼、反trump<br />\n而KW最大影響力就係喺嗰堆後生度<br />\n出兩款潮鞋、潮衫、搵Kim喺ig講兩句，<br />\n入屋過10個傳統選舉廣告"},{"pid":"655ba67beb9f8dbad44806f4587f04ecdb6e6dc3","tid":2156693,"uid":58841,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T15:20:34.000Z","msg":"𠝹票<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dce93b68dd5d1611099344ebe16f4276caf4645","tid":2156693,"uid":3241,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T15:24:07.000Z","msg":"同共匪養熱狗出黎等你地鬼打鬼一樣"},{"pid":"bb0ed38910f28141a7ccf76b0590cac7770690b0","tid":2156693,"uid":21545,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T15:26:13.000Z","msg":"美式大熱狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f739c1ac7a9525251f00b771166b849ec718efe","tid":2156693,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T15:27:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"307f5953ec5a54d2b339b93714882068a36445e4","tid":2156693,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T16:04:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8314642326aedf8b41e22dde36839f831829ba3","tid":2156693,"uid":68080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T16:07:40.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n咁玩咪介到侵票"}]